                        <join result="offenceVictim" targOrder="Y" targets="t17780603-69-off330 t17780603-69-victim538"></join>
                     </persName>
                     
                   on the <rs id="t17780603-69-cd331" type="crimeDate">2d of May</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17780603-69-off330 t17780603-69-cd331"></join>, that the said Richard with his hands and feet feloniously, wilfully, and of his malice afore-thought, did cast and throw the said 
                     <persName id="t17780603-69-person539">
                        James
                         Lefevre
                     <interp inst="t17780603-69-person539" type="surname" value="Lefevre"></interp>
